  "Description": {
    "English": "Highly prized and lustrous alloy. Popular with traders of all known primary galactic races. Crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ionized Cobalt</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Phosphorus</span>.<br><br>Easily recognizable by its bright red glow and strong magnetic field.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "柔软光亮的珍贵合金，深受所有已知的星系主要种族的商人喜爱。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">离子钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">磷</span>制作。<br><br>由于散发明亮的红光和强磁场而很容易辨认。",
    "TencentChinese": "柔软光亮的珍贵合金，深受所有已知的星系主要种族的商人喜爱。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">离子钴</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">磷</span>制作。<br><br>由于散发明亮的红光和强磁场而很容易辨认。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "價值極高、有著豐富光澤的合金。所有主要銀河種族貿易商都十分重視。由<span class=\"name name-earth\">離子化鈷</span>與<span class=\"name name-earth\">磷</span>製造而成。<br><br>明亮的紅色光澤與強烈的磁性，是其特色。"
  },
